::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe coughs, opening his eyes as a hot feeling spreads over his lungs. 
He coughs again, seeing a femm sitting by a fire as the room comes into 
focus. He roars, jumping up to his feet and falling forward immediately as 
dizzines spreads over him.

"What did you do to me?" he says in his deadly whisper, breathing heavilly as 
he looks at Zyber, his head laying on the ground.
